						               													<description>Loot Doodles is a print &amp;amp; play game in which you sail to various islands and collect treasures. At the beginning of the game, you draw your ship on the map. In each of the four rounds, you sail to up to four islands and take one resource (decided by which port you sail to, by drawing a line onto the map). After each round, you return to your ship and deliver the treasure. &amp;#10;However, the lines you draw may not cross each other, so you will have to plan ahead carefully. Also, ports on each island are numbered I to III, and you cannot go to the same number or to a different port on the same island twice in a row. For each resource you grab you get points. The goal is to score as many points as possible during the four rounds.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;In the multiplayer game, players keep their maps hidden. They take turns being the captain and announcing the number of the port everyone has to sail to.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Players can use one of the maps included in the game, or draw their own at the beginning of the game.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
